dev.jeka.core.api.depmanagement.artifact

Class JkSuppliedFileArtifactProducer<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.jeka.core.api.depmanagement.artifact.JkSuppliedFileArtifactProducer<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JkArtifactLocator, JkArtifactProducer

    public class JkSuppliedFileArtifactProducer<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements JkArtifactProducer
    This JkArtifactProducer produces artifacts files at the path provided by the caller

    To add artifacts to produce, caller has to provide the Path where is generated artifact along the Runnable for generating it.
